videos.description: Zack Moss rushes for 3 yards into the end zone for a Utah TD.
videos.headline: Moss' TD puts Utes first on the board

videos.description: Tyler Huntley finds Darren Carrington II down the sideline for a 25-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Carrington grabs it over defender in the end zone

videos.description: Devon Modster completes to Theo Howard who makes a one-handed catch for a 26-yard gain.
videos.headline: Howard stretches out for amazing one-handed grab

videos.description: Devon Modster connects with Darren Andrews for a 24-yard touchdown to close the gap on Utah.
videos.headline: Modster to Andrews gives UCLA first TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley finds Troy McCormick wide open down the sideline for a Utah touchdown.
videos.headline: McCormick scores huge 75-yard TD

videos.description: Zack Moss rushes 20 yards to the end zone to extend Utah's lead.
videos.headline: Moss breaks through for a 20-yard TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley connects with Siaosi Wilson down the middle to put the Utes in the red zone.
videos.headline: Huntley finds Wilson for 43-yard gain

videos.description: Tyler Huntley completes to Troy McCormick for a 13-yard Utah touchdown.
videos.headline: Huntley to McCormick for second TD

videos.description: Matt Lynch finds Eldridge Massington for a 5-yard Bruins' touchdown.
videos.headline: Lynch to Massington closes gap on Utes

videos.description: Tyler Huntley connects with Cody Ippolito for an Utes 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Huntley tosses fourth TD pass
